    "headline": "DOJ clears Paramount Skydance’s $110 billion Warner Bros. deal - report",
    "summary": "The unconditional clearance removes the primary federal regulatory hurdle standing between the two media giants and what would be one of the largest media combinations in history. Politico's report was corroborated by Newsmax and Quiver Quantitative, each also citing people familiar with the matter, though an official DOJ press release had not been published as of this writing.",
